---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import handShake from "../../public/icons/handshake.svg";
import user from "../../public/icons/user.svg";
---

<Layout
  metaDescription="Practical coaching and courses to strengthen clarity, confidence and performance at work — tailored individual support from StephBe."
  metaKeywords="individual coaching, performance coaching, career coaching, leadership coaching, StephBe"
  title="Individual Performance — StephBe"
  ogUrl="https://stephbe.ie/individual-performance/"
  classMain="individuals"
>
  <section class="hero-section">
    <h1>Strengthen Your Performance at Work</h1>
    <h4>For individuals ready to think clearly, perform consistently and raise their standards.</h4>
    <p>
      I spend my time helping organisations create cultures where people thrive. The same principles apply when working
      with individuals. Whether you're leading a team, changing career or simply trying to perform at your best, my
      coaching combines strategic thinking, practical tools and behavioural science to help you move forward with
      confidence.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-section">
      <a href="#courses-programmes" class="btn">Start a Course</a>
      <a
        class="btn"
        data-cal-link="stephbe/private-coaching-clients"
        data-cal-namespace="private-coaching-clients"
        data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'>Book a Discovery Call</a
      >
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="performance">
    <h2>Performance Goes Beyond Capability</h2>
    <p>
      Performance at work isn’t just about capability it’s shaped by clarity, behaviour and the environment you operate
      in.
    </p>
    <p>
      This page brings together a range of practical resources and targeted support designed to help you strengthen how
      you think, lead and perform.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="courses-programmes" id="courses-programmes">
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Courses & Programmes</h2>
      <p>
        Structured, practical learning designed to help you cut through noise and apply what matters. Every programme
        combines practical tools with insights from coaching, neuroscience and organisational psychology, helping you
        create change that lasts rather than relying on motivation alone.​
      </p>
      <div class="courses-grid">
        <article class="course-card">
          <h3>Living Your Values</h3>
          <p>Turn insight into action making clearer decisions and aligning how you work with what matters most.</p>
          <a
            href="https://stephanie-s-school-37db.thinkific.com/courses/light-up-your-life-with-your-values"
            target="_blank"
          >
            → View Course
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="course-card">
          <h3>Strengths & Transferable Skills</h3>
          <p>Get clear on your strengths and use them with confidence in new roles, interviews and career moves.</p>
          <a
            href="https://stephanie-s-school-37db.thinkific.com/courses/transferable-skills-stay-in-your-lane-while-being-brilliant"
            target="_blank"
          >
            → View Course
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="course-card">
          <h3>Staying on Track</h3>
          <p>Maintain focus, follow through on your goals and build consistency in how you work.</p>
          <a
            href="https://stephanie-s-school-37db.thinkific.com/courses/staying-the-course-how-to-keep-on-track-with-your-goals"
            target="_blank"
          >
            → View Course
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="course-card">
          <h3>Motivation & Momentum</h3>
          <p>Build the focus and energy needed to take action and sustain progress.</p>
          <a
            href="https://stephanie-s-school-37db.thinkific.com/courses/motivation-and-how-to-get-more-of-it"
            target="_blank"
          >
            → View Course
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="course-card">
          <h3>Self-Leadership</h3>
          <p>Strengthen your ability to manage your thinking, behaviour and performance at work.</p>
          <a
            href="https://stephanie-s-school-37db.thinkific.com/courses/get-out-of-your-own-way-and-become-your-own-best-friend"
            target="_blank"
          >
            → View Course
          </a>
        </article>
        <article class="course-card">
          <h3>Setting Clear Goals</h3>
          <p>Define focused, meaningful goals that guide action and improve follow-through.</p>
          <a href="https://stephanie-s-school-37db.thinkific.com/courses/setting-great-goals" target="_blank">
            → View Course
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="flexible">
    <h3>Flexible Support, Designed Around You</h3>
    <p>One session or ongoing support that’s entirely up to you.</p>
    <div class="btn-section">
      <a
        class="btn-third"
        data-cal-link="stephbe/private-coaching-clients"
        data-cal-namespace="private-coaching-clients"
        data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'>Book a Discovery Call</a
      >
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="coaching">
    <div class="title">
      <h2>One Session or Numerous</h2>
      <p>That's entirely up to you. Book a discovery call to explore the right path for you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contents">
      <div class="content">
        <Image class="logo" src={handShake} alt="" />
        <h3>Interview Coaching: One & Done</h3>
        <p>
          A focused, high-impact session designed to prepare you for a specific interview sharpening your message,
          increasing your confidence and elevating your delivery. Let’s help you to stand out from the crowd.
        </p>
        <!-- <a href="" target="_blank">Book your Session here → </a> -->
        <div class="btn-section">
          <a
            class="btn"
            data-cal-link="stephbe/private-coaching-clients"
            data-cal-namespace="private-coaching-clients"
            data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'>Book your Session here</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <Image class="logo" src={user} alt="" />
        <h3>Focused 1:1 Support</h3>
        <p>
          For those who want more tailored support, I offer a limited number of private sessions focused on clarity,
          decision-making and performance at work. These sessions are practical, structured and designed to create
          immediate impact.
        </p>
        <!-- <a href="" target="_blank">Enquire About Availability → </a> -->
        <div class="btn-section">
          <a
            class="btn"
            data-cal-link="stephbe/private-coaching-clients"
            data-cal-namespace="private-coaching-clients"
            data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'>Enquire About Availability</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-coaching">
    <h2>Why Coaching?</h2>
    <p>People consider coaching for many reasons.</p>
    <p>
      Sometimes it’s about performance, thinking more clearly, making better decisions or preparing for a specific
      moment.
    </p>
    <p>
      Other times, something feels off. They’re in roles that no longer fit, but feel stuck between staying and not
      knowing what comes next. Or they’ve stepped into something bigger and find themselves second-guessing their
      thinking, over-preparing or questioning whether they’re really ready, despite clear evidence that they are.
    </p>
    <p>Over time, this can show up as frustration, hesitation or a sense of being underutilised.</p>
    <p>
      This work creates the space to step back, think clearly and move forward with confidence, whether that means
      performing better where you are, or making a change.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
